383
00:21:45.340 --> 00:21:46.906
Q and a?

384
00:21:46.930 --> 00:21:48.736
That's… that's funny.

385
00:21:48.760 --> 00:21:50.116
She's funny. Who knew?

386
00:21:50.140 --> 00:21:51.720
