399
00:22:30.850 --> 00:22:33.100
- Elena.
- I know her name.

400
00:22:36.690 --> 00:22:39.916
- I take it you two are…
- what? No. What?

401
00:22:39.940 --> 00:22:41.666
Yeah. yeah. yeah. Because that…

402
