457
00:25:21.770 --> 00:25:24.666
- Really? Is that what it is?
- Yeah. I brought my best material.

458
00:25:24.690 --> 00:25:27.810
- So it's all downhill from here?
- Yeah. pretty much.

459
00:25:29.900 --> 00:25:31.150
God.

460
