fucking logistically…

477
00:26:28.420 --> 00:26:33.316
We'd all probably just give up
and still be in our lousy marriages.

478
00:26:33.340 --> 00:26:36.010
Then where would we be?

479
00:26:38.220 --> 00:26:40.220
